Chapter\xa0III Section\xa04, Chapter\xa0V, Chapter\xa0VII and Chapter\xa0XII and Article\xa078 shall apply from 2\xa0August 2025, with the exception of Article\xa0101;
(c)
Article\xa06(1) and the corresponding obligations in this Regulation shall apply from 2\xa0August 2027.
This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
