the evaluation and review of this Regulation pursuant to Article\xa0112, including as regards the serious incident reports referred to in Article\xa073, and the functioning of the EU database referred to in Article\xa071, the preparation of the delegated or implementing acts, and as regards possible alignments of this Regulation with the Union harmonisation legislation listed in Annex\xa0I;
